{"id":"676176d362e0497044079f4c","typeName":"AssaultRifle","category":"weapon","parentTypeChain":["AssaultRifle","Weapon","CompoundItem","Item"],"handbook":{"categoryId":"5b5f78fc86f77409407a7f90","price":29422},"common":{"name":{"zh":"FN SCAR-H X-17 7.62x51突击步枪","en":"FN SCAR-H X-17 7.62x51 assault rifle"},"shortName":{"zh":"X-17","en":"X-17"},"description":{"zh":"FN SCAR-H（特种作战部队战斗突击步枪-重型的缩写）突击步枪发射7.62×51毫米北约步枪弹，美国特种作战司令部采用的型号被命名为Mk 17型。该枪标配可侧向折叠的聚合物枪托与自由浮置式冷锻军规枪管，内膛镀有硬铬。SCAR只需简单改装便可切换拉机柄方向，而其余所有操作皆为双面对称，适应任何习惯的射手在任何场景下的射击姿势。机匣顶部集成有标准皮卡汀尼导轨，护木还另外设有三条附件导轨，可安装多种瞄具、战术灯和激光装置。由FN 赫斯塔尔公司设计制造，X Products公司在此基础上打造了X-17下机匣，以使用AR-10规格的弹匣。","en":"The FN SCAR-H (Special Operations Forces Combat Assault Rifle - Heavy) assault rifle chambered in 7.62x51 NATO rounds, was adopted by the US SOCOM as the Mk 17. Features a side-folding polymer stock and a free-floating, cold hammer-forged Mil-Spec barrel with hardchromed bore. Fully-ambidextrous operating controls instantly adapt the SCAR to any user or any shooting position. The receiver-integrated optical rail plus three accessory rails enable mounting of a wide variety of scopes, electronic sights, tactical lights and lasers. The X-17 lower receiver allows the installation of AR-10 magazines. Manufactured by Fabrique Nationale Herstal and X Products."},"weight":0.81,"width":1,"height":1,"rarity":"Superrare","backgroundColor":"black"},"properties":{"_raw":{"AdjustCollimatorsToTrajectory":false,"AimPlane":0.16,"AimSensitivity":0.65,"AllowFeed":true,"AllowJam":true,"AllowMisfire":true,"AllowOverheat":true,"AllowSlide":true,"AnimationVariantsNumber":0,"BackgroundColor":"black","BaseMalfunctionChance":0.183425,"BoltAction":false,"BurstShotsCount":3,"CameraSnap":4,"CameraToWeaponAngleSpeedRange":{"x":0.1,"y":0.2,"z":0},"CameraToWeaponAngleStep":0.1,"CanPutIntoDuringTheRaid":true,"CanQueueSecondShot":true,"CanRequireOnRagfair":false,"CanSellOnRagfair":true,"CanUnloadAmmoByPlayer":true,"CantRemoveFromSlotsDuringRaid":[],"CenterOfImpact":0